headline: WARP is here (sorry it took so long)
keywords: Birthday Week, Product News, WARP, 1.1.1.1, VPN, Speed & Reliability, DNS
description: Today, after a longer than expected wait, we're opening WARP and WARP+ to the general public. If you haven’t heard about it yet, WARP is a mobile app designed for everyone which uses our global network to secure all of your phone’s Internet traffic.
